{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155880/extras/Features_700_x_60.png?t=1659692213\" /><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>BUILD</strong></h2></u><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A survival strategy game where you build, craft, gather resources during the day.<br></li><li>Place buildings and design your own city layouts.<br></li><li>The positioning of these buildings can be vital to manage certain resources and affects gameplay. </li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155880/extras/timelapse-small.png?t=1659692213\" /><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SURVIVE</strong></h2></u><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Defend your settlement from monsters like wolves, chupacabra, spiders, and Tribal enemies.<br></li><li>Different bosses for each enemy type. Random enemies are spawned each night.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155880/extras/night_small.png?t=1659692213\" /><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore</strong></h2></u><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A randomly generated world-map to explore with ships.<br></li><li>Find cities to trade with and random encounters and loot.<br></li><li>We have plans to expand more in the world map post-launch.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155880/extras/Rain2_Small.png?t=1659692213\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155880/extras/Worldmap2_small.png?t=1659692213\" /><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Procedural Characters</strong></h2></u><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Every character unit has stats such as Strength, agility intelligence.<br></li><li>Every character has unique personality skills. <br></li><li>Managing health, energy, and hunger is key to the survival of units.</li></ul><i